narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: The course is fairly fast-paced, but not very difficult. The course is designed to have a consistent amount of work each night, and the exams are fairly straightforward.
I definitely learned a lot but it was very difficult
If you want to learn and speak Spanish than this a good class to take. Be ready to work everyday though.
